title: Bug 109350: Output parameter should display in data set dialog
OB: While on the query result page, no data is returned. The actual result should be that the output parameter is displayed in the edit data set dialog.
EB: Bug 109350: Output parameter should be displayed in the data set dialog. The output parameter should also be displayed in the edit data set dialog.
SR: To reproduce: call the stored procedure from an Oracle database, where the query result is stored in the output parameter as an object. On the query result page, observe that no data is returned. The output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog.
